ectool logs given ectool command lines for reference and reuse.

projectcommands lists the property path to each command in steps of the
given project.  The command may not exist, since it does not yet check.

projectsteps lists steps for each procedure of the given project.

redirect searches for /git/*/sh-inferno scripts and runs them, since
Inferno has no $PATH.

workflowtrans lists states and transitions of the given project's
given workflow.  It decorates transitions with the target state,
and each state with its (subprocedure) or [subworkflow].
(If the sub is in another project, it is prepended to the name
and separated with a colon.)
